+fluent-package (6.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low
+
+  * New upstream release.
+
+ -- Kentaro Hayashi <hayashi@clear-code.com>  Fri, 29 Aug 2025 13:55:06 -0000
+
 fluent-package (5.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=low
 
   * New upstream release.
